data.description: VIEWS! VIEWS! THREE BEDROOMS, FAMILY ROOM, OFFICE, TWO DINING AREAS, TWO FULL BATHS PLUS A HALF BATH, TWO BAY GARAGE, THIRD GARAGE/SHOP, FOURTH OUTDOOR TOOLS GARAGE, SPARKLING IN-GROUND POOL, SUNROOM, FOUR SIDES BRICK AND STONE, REFRIGERATOR, WASHER AND DRYER INCLUDED * This stunning custom home on 5.41 acres has been immaculately maintained. Cool off in the sparkling, in-ground pool that is completely private and is professionally maintained. There are many outdoor entertaining options with multiple sitting areas, covered patios, and meticulously landscaped acres with mature shade trees, shrubs, and stone-lined flower beds. The large circular driveway in front doubles as an additional patio. * Inside you will find a dream home with an open floor plan. The kitchen is elaborately done with ornate stonework, granite countertops and breakfast bar, glass cooktop, built-in microwave, built-in oven, under-cabinet lighting, and a pantry. The family room features a ceiling fan and propane fireplace with mantle and hearth. There is a formal dining room and an everyday dining area. * The split floor plan allows privacy for the owners. The master suite has a ceiling fan, walk-in closet, private door to the pool area, and luxurious master bath with a jetted tub and redwood wet sauna. * The third car garage is a shop with a heating/air conditioning unit that is included. On the other side of the home is a garage bay for outdoor tools and toys. Please visit the virtual tour for videos.
